Notes on bundled content:
- Music and sound effects are generated procedurally at runtime via the Web
  Audio API; no third-party audio files are included or required.
- Visuals use CSS, inline SVG, and system emoji; no third-party image assets
  are included.
- "Sahelia" and all in-game text are original and fictional.
